sion the implementation of this feature adding a new option to the `AdvertiseOptions` class. Then, on publication we would have to decide if drop the message or publish it.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Implement message throttling in the publisher side to be able to control the number of messages published by a node. Take a look at issue <a href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/issues/2/message-throttling-on-the-subscriber\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Message throttling on the subscriber\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#2</s></a> and <a href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pull-requests/174/add-message-throttling-in-the-subscriber\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #174</a> for a similar feature implemented on the subscriber side.</p>\n<p>I envision the implementation of this feature adding a new option to the <code>AdvertiseOptions</code> class. Then, on publication we would have to decide if drop the message or publish it.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Atul Sharma", "uuid": "{12fad606-5e78-4769-9cd4-2c66061e0734}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B12fad606-5e78-4769-9cd4-2c66061e0734%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B12fad606-5e78-4769-9cd4-2c66061e0734%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:0d900363-1a31-4670-a99d-a155d4e5f4a1/0880ff8d-e752-47ad-bae9-7b20fbae0a87/128"}}, "nickname": "Karishma", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:0d900363-1a31-4670-a99d-a155d4e5f4a1"}, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2016-09-23T20:37:49.947957+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2017-01-09T22:37:50.869282+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 56}